Sentencas: BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 - alpha solid electrolyte was prepared by high-temperature solid state reaction and its ionic conduction was investigated by means of hydrogen concentration cell and oxygen concentration cell.
Titulo: Ionic conduction in BaCeO0.8Y0.2O3-α and its performance of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: as a solid electrolyte and porous platinum as electrodes, hydrogen-air fuel cell was constructed and the I-V characteristic of the fuel cell was determined.
Titulo: Ionic conduction in BaCeO0.8Y0.2O3-α and its performance of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: It was found that BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 - alpha exhibited the almost pure protonic conduction under hydrogen gas and a mixed conduction of oxide-ion and electron hole under oxygen gas, and that the fuel cell exhibited good and stable performance in the temperature range of 600 similar to 1000 degreesC. The open-circuit voltage (OCV) is close to the theoretical value.
Titulo: Ionic conduction in BaCeO0.8Y0.2O3-α and its performance of solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The maximum current output and the maximum power output from the cell were about 680mA .
